        <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-2">May 2025</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Spring 2025 Cohort Completes BID Analyses</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">The Spring 2025 cohort has completed their analysis of five different NYC BIDs: Downtown Brooklyn, DUMBO Improvement District, 5th Avenue in Brooklyn, Long Island City, and the West Village.</p>
      </div>
      
