        <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-2">April 2025</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Interactive Map Experience Enhanced</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">We've optimized our BID Map Explorer for better performance and smoother interactions, allowing you to navigate NYC's Business Improvement Districts more seamlessly than ever.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="container text-center fade-in">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to explore the data?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl opacity-90 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Dive into our comprehensive analyses of Business Improvement Districts across New York City.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href={`${base}/projects`} class="px-8 py-3 bg-white text-primary font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-opacity-95 transition-colors">
          View All Projects
